lead_paragraph: Lindsey Cunningham hit three 3-pointers and finished with 16 points to lead the 22nd-ranked Missouri women past LSU 52-46 Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Cunningham, No. 22 Missouri Women Beat LSU 52-46
